  m_text: 'A square pyramid is formed when the base of the pyramid is in the shape
    of a square. A square pyramid consists of one square base and three triangular
    faces. In other words, it has 8 edges, 5 vertices, and 4 faces.


    <b>Formula:
    <i>V=(1/3)lwh</i></b>'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 2e498d1c8094910479dc3e1b768306a4, type: 2}
